---------------------------------------------------------

How to use basic
1.Fine some chapter of 3-kingdoms link or file(put in data and skip preprocessing)
2.run ner for analysis character
3.run relationship_extraction.py then you'll wait processing just a minutes
4.If finish processing go to output folder,You must found JSON file in chapter_relations_rulebased or graphs in graphs folder

